T products</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6ada93c22d8b">
<p local-id=3D"899b272021e2">Based on this mapping we have 2 products in DB=
 and share the same data to front end</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"038f952d02bd">
<p local-id=3D"f2d583082e6a">For PB Retailer / Influencer we show only 3 op=
tions in Navbar - Home, Cart and Order</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"25a6a706ef5f">
<p local-id=3D"d86196ff51e9">On click of banners we navigate to PLP Page wi=
th only PB TMT products</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7893d6d2bf62">
<p local-id=3D"508842e71b5a"><strong>Search does not handle only PB TMT pro=
